<h3 id="about-the-script">About the script</h3>

<p>I have coded my bash script for automatically downloading multiple exploits directly to the local machine based on given bash argument with single enter key click from official <a href="https://exploit-db.com">exploit-db website</a>.</p>

<p>My script deals with exploits from exploit-db so make sure that <a href="https://github.com/offensive-security/exploitdb">searchsploit</a> is installed in the machine.</p>

